        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6892921-peter?shelf=law">law</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6892921-peter?shelf=free-speech">free-speech</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer295786629" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3615005296490089547">Geoffrey Robertson QC has written a truly fascinating overview of his career defending artists, publishers, poets, civil servants who have fallen foul (or been accused of falling foul) of laws to curb their free speech.<br/><br/>Heartily recommended for lawyers or those with an interest in the subject.</span>

          </span>
